{"tid":2370621,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"研究人員：Apple Watch 可於 COVID-19 病徵出現前一週檢測出疾病 $AAPL","createTime":"2021-01-18T07:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T08:23:46.000Z","uid":2638,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"30d45b11697fcfddaaa559460d81219a33ca45f5","tid":2370621,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:20:52.000Z","msg":"COVID-19 的疫情在經過去年一整年的肆虐之後，今年初不但沒有趨緩，反而又傳出有變種病毒的問題。而現在，美國西奈山醫療系統和史丹佛大學的研究指出，對 COVID-19 呈陽性反應的人士有可能藉由 Apple Watch 等智慧型手錶在症狀出現前的一週以前發現疾病。<br />\n<br />\n研究表明人體的心率會隨著體內的發炎而產生變化，COVID-19 亦如此。因此對 COVID-19 呈陽性反應的人在配戴 Apple Watch、Garmin 和 Fitbit 等智慧型手錶後，有 81% 的人於症狀發作前的最多 9 天半以前就出現了靜態心率上升的情況。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，透過智慧型手錶的數據發現有三分之二的案例是在病徵出現前的 4 到 7 天就得以檢測出 COVID-19，顯示智慧型手錶在防疫上可能可以提供相當大的幫助。"},{"pid":"5d177de1b79193acbde8b9c444f58fb1de233b07","tid":2370621,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:27:17.000Z","msg":"一人送一隻apple watch 防疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1b942f23ddbd89cedee78b71b05893333d1c91","tid":2370621,"uid":330227,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"5d177de1b79193acbde8b9c444f58fb1de233b07","tid":2370621,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:27:17.000Z","msg":"一人送一隻apple watch 防疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n此apple watch 是由香港政府監管和管理。"},{"pid":"d674b0f69b6a55b9e829c057edb04ad649be4af7","tid":2370621,"uid":5686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d177de1b79193acbde8b9c444f58fb1de233b07","tid":2370621,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:27:17.000Z","msg":"一人送一隻apple watch 防疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:23:46.000Z","msg":"小米手環"}]}